Tujhe Kitna Chaahne Lage Hum❤️
Keys : @kkeval_music07 
Special thanks : @dhaval_shale @mohinidave
It's the Month of Love , and I have been feeling a bit too giddy as well. Not because I am in love with someone, but maybe because I have no reason to not be in love. 
So, today, and maybe everyday, I hope you remember to be grateful for your health and wellness and fall in love with your body. 
I hope you remember to love your parents and spend quality time with them just chatting over chaai and naashta. 
I hope you remember to annoy your siblings and take pleasure out of those little fights and dramatic arguments. 
I hope you find something you love to do and fight to do it everyday and still never get tired of it. 
I hope you remember to plan hangouts with your friends, go out to eat, tease the hell outta them and never get tired of their company. 
But most of all, I hope you look in the mirror and see the person you love the most staring lovingly back at you ✨💕
